<header>
<div class="dnd_container dnd_container__heading">
<h1>More on Granta.com</h1>
</div>
</header>
<div class="dnd_section_content">
<div class="dnd_container">
<div class="dnd_column_dd_span4">
<div class="dnd_post-card">
<div class="dnd_post-card__upper-section">
<h6 class="dnd_post-card__category-text">
<a href="https://granta.com/explore?cat=essays-and-memoir"><span class="dnd_post-card__red-text">Essays &amp; Memoir </span></a>
<span class="dnd_post-card__divider">|</span>
<a href="https://granta.com/products/granta-167"><span>Issue 167</span></a>
<span class="dnd_post-card__padlock"></span>
</h6>
<a href="https://granta.com/sinking-town/">
<div data-bg="https://granta.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Kumar_banner.jpg" class="dnd_post-card_img background-align__middle rocket-lazyload" data-background="https://granta.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Kumar_banner.jpg" style></div>
</a>
</div>
<div class="dnd_post-card__lower-section">
<h2 class="dnd_post-card_title">
<a href="https://granta.com/sinking-town/">
Sinking Town
</a>
</h2>
<h4 class="dnd_post-card_author">
<a class="contributor-link" href="https://granta.com/contributor/amitava-kumar/">Amitava Kumar</a>
</h4>
<p class="dnd_post-card_text">
The towns fate was tied to poor development and ecological disaster. <br/> <br/> Amitava Kumar visits a Himalayan town.
</p>
</div>
</div> </div>
<div class="dnd_column_dd_span4">
<div class="dnd_post-card">
<div class="dnd_post-card__upper-section">
<h6 class="dnd_post-card__category-text">
<a href="https://granta.com/explore?cat=essays-and-memoir"><span class="dnd_post-card__red-text">Essays &amp; Memoir </span></a>
