<a href="https://granta.com/you-are-the-product-dalla-rosa/">
<div data-bg="https://granta.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/extraction-feature-4-scaled.jpg" class="dnd_post-card_img background-align__middle rocket-lazyload" data-background="https://granta.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/extraction-feature-4-scaled.jpg" style></div>
</a>
</div>
<div class="dnd_post-card__lower-section">
<h2 class="dnd_post-card_title">
<a href="https://granta.com/you-are-the-product-dalla-rosa/">
You Are the Product
</a>
</h2>
<h4 class="dnd_post-card_author">
<a class="contributor-link" href="https://granta.com/contributor/paul-dalla-rosa/">Paul Dalla Rosa</a>
</h4>
<p class="dnd_post-card_text">
I have a pathological addiction to the internet, which I indulge with the excuse of making art. It rarely translates to anything good and mostly leaves me overstimulated and afraid.<br/><br/>Paul Dalla Rosa on excess and the internet.
</p>
</div>
</div> </div>
<div class="dnd_column_dd_span4">
<div class="dnd_post-card">
<div class="dnd_post-card__upper-section">
<h6 class="dnd_post-card__category-text">
