</a>
</div>
<div class="dnd_post-card__lower-section">
<h2 class="dnd_post-card_title">
<a href="https://granta.com/you-are-the-product-mclaughlin/">
You Are the Product
</a>
</h2>
<h4 class="dnd_post-card_author">
<a class="contributor-link" href="https://granta.com/contributor/rosanna-mclaughlin/">Rosanna McLaughlin</a>
</h4>
<p class="dnd_post-card_text">
Like pretty much everyone who uses the internet, I have seen many terrible things that I did not search for and that I cannot unsee.<br/><br/>Rosanna McLaughlin on what the internet thinks she wants.
</p>
